          "settings": {
            "title": "WHAT IS YOUR RETURN POLICY?",
            "htmlContent": "",
            "content": "<p> Items should be returned within 30 days of delivery, in original saleable condition, unworn, unwashed, with all tags still attached and in original packaging. All items are inspected on return, returns that are refused will be posted back to you.<br/><br/><strong>Please keep your proof of return to allow you/ us to track your parcel and investigate any returns that go missing, without the tracking we are unable to investigate.</strong><br/><br/>*Abuse of our Returns Policy (including repeated refunds, free wardrobing and chargeback fraud) will NOT be accepted. Gym King reserves the right to make the final decision on returns and refunds and reserve the right to close a customer account if we deem it necessary.</p>"
          }
        },
        "card_N7QwAC": {
          "type": "card",
          "settings": {
            "title": "DO YOU OFFER EXCHANGES?",
            "htmlContent": "",
            "content": "<p>Sorry we don't offer exchanges, your returned items will be refunded.</p>"
          }
        },
        "card_xUcYGC": {
          "type": "card",
          "settings": {
            "title": "WHAT ITEMS CANNOT BE RETURNED?",
            "htmlContent": "",
            "content": "<p>The following are exceptions to the return policy above :</p><ul><li>If an item is marked as Final Sale, this item is non-returnable.</li><li>Women’s swimwear can only be returned if the hygiene seal is still intact and has not been removed.</li><li>Socks can be returned if they are <strong>sealed</strong> in their original packaging.</li><li>Men’s swimwear, underwear and Women's underwear cannot be returned for hygiene reasons.</li><li>All Bottles are non-returnable due to hygiene reasons.</li></ul>"
          }
        },
        "card_Btgaz4": {
          "type": "card",
          "settings": {
            "title": "HOW DO I RETURN MY ITEMS?",
            "htmlContent": "",
            "content": "<ul><li>Access our easy <a href=\"https://gymkingmarketplace.returns.international/\">return portal</a></li><li>You will need your Marketplace order number (which should be on your order confirmation) and postcode/email address which can be found on the paperwork in your parcel.</li><li>Follow the instructions to create your return and generate your return label/ QR code.</li><li>Put your item(s) in your parcel, seal it securely and affix your return label (if you opted to print it).</li><li>Take your parcel to your chosen Evri Parcelshop location</li></ul><p><strong>If your order is past 30 days you will be unable to raise a return on the portal. Please contact your Marketplace customer services with your order number and your reason for return.</strong></p><p><strong>Please keep hold of your receipt/drop off email as it has your tracking information and we would be unable to investigate and issues without it.</strong></p>"
          }
        },
