            "title": "WHEN WILL I GET MY REFUND?",
            "htmlContent": "",
            "content": "<p>We process your returns as quickly as we can and usually do so within 7 days of receipt. During busy periods this may take up to 14 days. Please also allow up to 5 working days for the refund to appear on your bank statement.</p>"
